What you need to know:

Muyah, who took over the reign at swimming in September 2016 upon the resignation of Ben Ekumbo, passed away on Tuesday morning at Kenyatta University HospitalKSF deputy president Zack Musembi confirmed that Muyah was admitted in the Intensive Care Unit (ICU) at Kenyatta University Hospital on March 29Muyah, 54, is survived by his wife and two children